Rallos Zek is not a 6 second fight, but he is a low HP mob.  Figure in 6 Wizards with Manaburn and you'll see why it would be very overpowered.  GG 6 minute fight.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>The reason I am now proposing this new skill is because I have all but given up on Manaburn itself being fixed. I'm hoping that a new AA requiring more AA points might meet the approval of Sony since it extends the life of the game for many by offering more XP sinks.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
First of all, with the exceptions of crits, Manaburn is not broken.  There is a huge difference between something not being desirable and it being broken.  Secondly, using what you said earlier in reply to someone saying they wouldn't use the new Manaburn, no one is forcing you to get Manaburn. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
