<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>If any of what you say is true, then why aren't you using the current MB for a free 9500 points of damage? That certainly beats the 6200 points of damage you stated that you do. You already said MB is free for you with your mana regen, so what's the problem? Isn't the current Manaburn already 'gimping' the encounter for you? If not, I fail to see why the new one would.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
